102
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:41,100
Great question, Jordan.

103
00:04:41,100 --> 00:04:42,230
You’re right.

104
00:04:42,230 --> 00:04:44,430
This is one of those weird things that both

105
00:04:44,430 --> 00:04:48,030
