agree on:

106
00:04:48,030 --> 00:04:52,389
that everything within the Nine-Dash Line
belongs to China.

107
00:04:52,389 --> 00:04:56,940
Though obviously they don’t agree on which
China that is.

108
00:04:56,940 --> 00:04:57,980
As you pointed out,

109
00:04:57,980 --> 00:05:00,340
Taiwan has had its own small island

110
00:05:00,340 --> 00:05:02,130
in the South China Sea for decades.

111
00:05:02,130 --> 00:05:04,520
It’s called Itu Aba.

112
00:05:04,520 --> 00:05:06,910
But Taiwan’s Coast Guard uses it mainly

113
00:05:06,910 --> 00:05:09,280
for search and rescue in the area—

114
00:05:09,280 --> 00:05:11,770
like to help a fishing boat that capsizes,

115
00:05:11,770 --> 00:05:13,870
no matter what country it’s from.

116
00:05:13,870 --> 00:05:17,950
See, when you build hospitals instead of missile
silos,

117
00:05:17,950 --> 00:05:20,750
