118
00:05:20,750 --> 00:05:23,010
Basically, the problem other countries have

119
00:05:23,010 --> 00:05:26,440
isn’t China’s historical claims to the
South China Sea.

120
00:05:26,440 --> 00:05:30,430
It’s the Chinese Communist Party being extremely
aggressive

121
00:05:30,430 --> 00:05:33,460
about building up islands for military use.

122
00:05:33,460 --> 00:05:37,990
Also, of course, we trust Taiwan because it’s
everyone’s ally.

123
00:05:37,990 --> 00:05:42,710
Whereas the PRC is, at best, a frenemy.

